title: International Travel and Migration: September 2015 (Statistics New Zealand)
text: ( Source : Statistics New Zealand ) In September 2015 compared with September 2014 : Visitor arrivals (217, 000 ) were up 23,700. The biggest changes were in arrivals from: Australia (up 10, 100 ) China (up 7, 500 ) Japan (up 1,200) the United States
